00:38:31.530 --> 00:38:38.050
You have to learn how to explain the future
in a way that people living in the past can

00:38:38.050 --> 00:38:39.050
embrace.

00:38:39.050 --> 00:38:40.330
That's where change happens.

00:38:40.330 --> 00:38:42.190
Going in there, "You're wrong.

00:38:42.190 --> 00:38:43.190
You're stupid.

00:38:43.190 --> 00:38:44.190
You don't get it."

00:38:44.190 --> 00:38:45.860
Tom Bilyeu: I came across that part in the
book.

00:38:45.860 --> 00:38:48.670
