00:39:19.590 --> 00:39:23.420
you get a step closer to what I think really
has made you so great and so successful, and

00:39:23.420 --> 00:39:28.300
this is certainly what turned me on so much
about your book, which is basically Ryan Holiday's

00:39:28.300 --> 00:39:30.310
