other country.

00:40:15.110 --> 00:40:22.920
My generation, it was I Love Lucy or Jackie
Gleason would have the get-rich-quick thing.

00:40:22.920 --> 00:40:24.700
Your generation, it was Homer Simpson.

00:40:24.700 --> 00:40:29.070
He's got this get-rich-quick scheme, it all
fails, and then life goes on.

00:40:29.070 --> 00:40:32.970
In the rest of the world, that life goes on
part isn't part of the dialogue.

00:40:32.970 --> 00:40:42.520
So we're a country that was made up of people
that came here overcoming odds for something

00:40:42.520 --> 00:40:44.590
better.

00:40:44.590 --> 00:40:47.369
That's that basic pioneer spirit.

00:40:47.369 --> 00:40:53.940
