00:41:02.020 --> 00:41:03.150
Everybody can benefit.

00:41:03.150 --> 00:41:06.450
Why wouldn't you want that?

00:41:06.450 --> 00:41:12.090
Tom Bilyeu: Talk to me about education because
you said that we educate our youth like it's

00:41:12.090 --> 00:41:13.670
a scarcity mindset.

00:41:13.670 --> 00:41:22.550
Jay Samit: It's fill-in-the-blank, measure,
